name: Unidentified_Twi%27lek_rebel
content: A Rutian Twi'lek rebel served as a member of the Alliance to Restore the Republic after the Battle of Hoth aboard the EF76 Nebulon-B escort frigate Redemption. Sometime after Starlight Squadron leader Lieutenant Shara Bey was forced to remain behind on the Imperial Star Destroyer Tarkin's Will in order for her squadron to leave with navigational data and other valuable intelligence the Alliance could use in their fight with the Empire, Bey's husband, Kes Dameron, asked the Twi'lek if there had been any word from Bey, to which the Twi'lek responded that there hadn't been any. A short while later, the Twi'lek informed General Leia Organa, who was speaking with Dameron, that Bey had sent a signal to them using the Trawak codes the rebels had recently established.
